 care. This centre will act as a conduit to educate and expose our community to the challenges and solutions associated with elder and hospice care and ensure equitable and caring treatment of all those we serve. The care partners employed will consistently deliver exceptional care and serve as role models for those to follow. True change begins by taking the first step in a different direction, and the model supporting this initiative will promote the change we need and deserve as a community.</p>'),(2167,100,'_flexible_2_simple_contents_1_content','field_627142eda2b07'),(2168,100,'flexible_2_simple_contents_2_content','<h3>ONE CARE CENTRE OFFERING MULTIPLE SERVICES</h3>\r\nA community care centre that focuses on living life to its fullest. Programmes and services developed around the needs of the residents and their families.\r\nPatient directed care.\r\nServices that extend into the community.\r\nPurposeful and meaningful activities for residents and the community.\r\nExceptional care delivered consistently with love &amp; compassion.\r\nAbility &amp; desire to change and adapt to resident\'s needs.\r\nA gateway to the community where multi-generational interaction is supported.\r\n\r\nA PLACE WE CAN ALL CALL HOME'),(2169,100,'_flexible_2_simple_contents_2_content','field_627142eda2b07'),(2170,101,'flexible','a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:8:\"cta_itab\";i:2;s:14:\"simple_content\";}'),(2171,101,'_flexible','field_6259dde8e2c55'),(2172,101,'flexible_0_slide_0_title','This is title'),(2173,101,'_flexible_0_slide_0_title','field_6259de4685dd5'),(2174,101,'flexible_0_slide_0_image',''),(2175,101,'_flexible_0_slide_0_image','field_6259de3385dd4'),(2176,101,'flexible_0_slide_0_subtitle','This is subtitle'),(2177,101,'_flexible_0_slide_0_subtitle','field_6259de7585dd6'),(2178,101,'flexible_0_slide_0_buttons_0_button','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:5:\"CTA 1\";s:3:\"url\";s:1:\"#\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(2179,101,'_flexible_0_slide_0_buttons_0_button','field_6259de8f85dd8'),(